    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2843469582" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer11866134416554562921">Unnecessarily repetitive and a bit wordy at times, this brick of a book did keep my attention for most of the long journey it took for me to read it, as the subject and the dive he takes to explore so called madness, goes very deep. Overall quite fascinating.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


